    .container
        h1 About Me
        p Hello, I have been playing Hypixel Skyblock since the first week of its release. I noticed that it's very important to get updated with the most profitable minions, so I decided to make a calculator myself.
        
        h2#acknowledgements.mt-5 Acknowledgements
        hr
        h3 Data source
        ul
            li <a href="https://api.hypixel.net">Hypixel API</a>
            li <a href="https://hypixel-skyblock.fandom.com/wiki/Minions">Hypixel SkyBlock Wiki</a>
            li <a href="https://hypixel.net/threads/spreadsheet-skyblock-minions-v1-7-added-sky-shiiyu-moe-importer.2166857/">Minions Sheet by TBlazeWarriorT </a>
            li <a href="https://hypixel.net/threads/api-bazaar-item-names-to-in-game-bazaar-item-json.2845357/">Item names JSON file by Bozosword and AkaCrafterCZ</a>
        p First of all, I would like to stress that without the Hypixel API, HyMinions would not exist. Not a lot of games have such a comprehensive and intuitive API like Hypixel, which resulted in a huge amount of community-created content on Skyblock. More content from the API would be appreciated, such as being able to know the current mayor, so that I can add mayor-specific events to the events timer, Jacob's Farming Contest farming materials, and a player's player upgrade in Community Center.
        p I know that lots of you are big fans of <a href="https://hypixel.net/threads/spreadsheet-skyblock-minions-v1-7-added-sky-shiiyu-moe-importer.2166857/">TBlazeWarriorT's minion spreadsheet</a>, and so am I! In fact, I would like to give my compliments to him as Hyminions won't be successful without the minion data provided by the spreadsheet. I would also like to thank <a href="https://hypixel-skyblock.fandom.com/wiki/Minions">Hypixel Skyblock Wiki</a> for listing out the data as well. Also, I would like to express my gratitude to <a href="https://hypixel.net/threads/api-bazaar-item-names-to-in-game-bazaar-item-json.2845357/">Bozosword and AkaCrafterCZ</a>, who created and maintained a JSON file to convert the item codes obtained from the bazaar Hypixel API to the conventional item names, long before the official API has it.
        
        br
        h3 Promotion
        p I would like to thank everybody who promoted my site. From the very first viewers through Hypixel forums to the two selected Youtubers below who sharply boosted the popularity of HyMinions through mentioning my website in their videos.
        ul
            li <a href="https://youtu.be/_LmqqJtsdrk"> ModernSoldier - Are Snow Minions Still The BEST MINION? | Hypixel Skyblock</a>
            li <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mhxDaMPsVxI">Tanker Man 3000 - Which Minion Makes The Most Money in Hypixel Skyblock? - Stop Using The Snow Minion.</a>
        p If you found this website useful, do <a href="https://discord.gg/2KabAgsN6Y">join my Discord</a> for more discussion and show it to your friends! Although recently inactive, I would try my best to keep everything here updated and as accurate as possible. Thank you for using my website.
        
        h2.mt-5 Disclaimer
        hr
        p As more people are using my website, I would like to explain more about how the minions profit calculator, minions crafts calculator and the forge calculator work and their limitations.
        p Please note that the calculators calculate based on the instantaneous price of the items sold at the bazaar, so the prices may fluctuate a lot from time to time, and so do the minions profit/cost (as we all know the economy of Skyblock is quite unstable). The "best minion" for money may not be the same some time later. I hope you all understand this uncertainty.
        p Overall speaking, snow minions and clay minions are the most stable for profit as their profits do not depend on the economy. If you would like to explore other relatively stable alternatives you may watch <a href="https://youtu.be/_LmqqJtsdrk"> ModernSoldier's video</a> for more advice.
        p As the volume of items in Auction House is much less than items in Bazaar, the risk would be much higher than using the minions profit calculator, as you may make a loss from forges if you are not careful. 

